A critical advantage of the Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite architecture for a SHRM prep system is its expansive context window. With an input token limit of 1,048,576 tokens, the model can ingest the entire SHRM BASK document, along with vast amounts of supplementary research and legal regulations, in a single prompt. This allows the model to generate highly contextualized questions and rationales that are irrefutably grounded in SHRM's specific best practices.
